query:
SELECT 
  u.id as userId, 
  u.email as userEmail,
  u.name as userName,
  j.id as jobId,
  j.customerId,
  j.customerEmail,
  j.customerName,
  j.status,
  j.serviceType
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN jobs j ON (j.customerId = u.id OR j.customerEmail = u.email)
WHERE u.email LIKE '%12%customer%'
ORDER BY j.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
